        public ServiceRequest(URL documentUrl,
                      SupportedMimeType type,

        Construct a request for the online service to annotate or classify a document downloaded directly from a remote URL.
        Parameters:
        documentUrl - The URL address of the document
        type - the MIME type that the service should use to parse the document.
        imageTagging - Whether to include image tagging in the response
        imageCategorization - Whether to include image categorization in the response
